Gaset moro miluongo ni Africa’s Cities: Opening Doors to the World, mondik gi World Bank, wacho niya; "Ok en adier ni ohelni ng'eny e taonde mag Afrika, kata ni ji odak maber kuno. Ji opong' thich e taondego ma ok dagre. “Ng'eny joma odak e taondego odak e gorofe machieko chieko kata mier mothung', moting'o ute matindo tindo maonge nderni malong'o, pi, kata stima."
